<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN"><html>  <head>    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="content-type">    <title></title>  </head>  <body class="c3 doc-content" style="background-color: #ffffff; max-width: 468pt; padding: 72pt 72pt 72pt 72pt;">    <p class="c18" style="background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 8pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">      <span class="c2" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">What is the first thing you do in the morning?</span>    </p>    <p class="c18" style="background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 8pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">      <span class="c2" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Do you stretch? Drink water? Or go to the bathroom?</span>    </p>    <p class="c18" style="background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 8pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">      <span class="c2" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">It may be a weird question&hellip;</span>    </p>    <p class="c18" style="background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 8pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">      <span class="c2" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">But new groundbreaking research reveals a surprising connection between neuropathy and your morning habit.</span>    </p>    <p class="c18" style="background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 8pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">      <span class="c0" style="font-weight: 700;">88,268 people</span> <span>&ndash; who had suffered from tingling, numbness, burning, and pain in their hands, feet, legs, and face &ndash; were shocked by how this simple</span><span class="c13 c0" style="color: #555555; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</span><span class="c12 c0" style="-webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; font-weight: 700;"><a href="hxxps://storage[.]googleapis[.]com/everrise/triumphway[.]html#4eiWPV96950QUPK425zmuioxkfqi32OEKIKASHBTKDXCF195982NIWL31885B7">9-second change</a></span><span class="c0 c13" style="color: #555555; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</span><span class="c2" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">to their morning routine could eliminate their nerve pain so quickly.</span>    </p>    <p class="c18" style="background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 8pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">      <span class="c2" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Something no prescription drugs, cream, patches, therapies, or doctor visits ever helped them do&hellip;</span>    </p>    <p class="c18" style="background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 8pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">      <span>Watch this</span><span class="c13 c0" style="color: #555555; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</span><span class="c12 c0" style="-webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; font-weight: 700;"><a href="hxxps://storage[.]googleapis[.]com/everrise/triumphway[.]html#4sIorV96950fRZv425tzrnaimbqf32QGPHMAMYXLPPUIN195982NVXJ31885s7">short video</a></span><span class="c13 c0" style="color: #555555; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</span><span>right now and find out the latest neuropathy breakthrough from</span> <span class="c0" style="font-weight: 700;">Columbia University and Harvard</span><span class="c2" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">.</span>    </p>    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 12pt; padding-top: 12pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">      <span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 287.50px; height: 212.67px;"><a href="hxxps://storage[.]googleapis[.]com/everrise/triumphway[.]html#4dJJyt96950aYGt425wtbdiibsac32DWWXHNJBXPWLIBR195982HQBY31885q7"><img border="0" alt="" src="hxxps://i[.]imgur[.]com/8nabrtJ[.]png" style="width: 287.50px; height: 212.67px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></a></span>    </p>    <p style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">      <br>      <font size="2"><br>     <tr>
